unchanged when compared to classical least-squares fitting methods. This can\npotentially have important consequences on the design of follow-up strategies\nof ongoing direct imaging surveys.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Apr 2016 20:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 22 Apr 2016 02:10:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-29"}
