hods to lift the\ncontraction for the limit equation to the extended phase space, including the\nvelocity and magnetic fields. Moreover, for the convergence of solutions at\nfinite times we make use of a probabilistic modification of the Gr\\\"onwall\ninequality, relying on a delicate stopping time argument.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Apr 2016 15:15:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-04-22"}
